



@deftypefun {int} {gnutls_openpgp_crt_check_email} (gnutls_openpgp_crt_t @var{key}, const char * @var{email}, unsigned @var{flags})
@var{key}: should contain a @code{gnutls_openpgp_crt_t}  type

@var{email}: A null terminated string that contains an RFC822 address (email)

@var{flags}: gnutls_certificate_verify_flags

This function will check if the given key's owner matches the
given email address. 

@strong{Returns:} non-zero for a successful match, and zero on failure.
@end deftypefun
